      "updated": 1780339848957,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional Requirements:\n- Users can upload huge 3DModels\n- Detect relevant elements in the model\n- Calculate routes for cargoes\n\nNon-Functional Requirements:\n- Support models with billions of triangles (60GB)\n- Fast route calculation for hundreds of cargoes",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional Requirements:\n- Users can upload huge 3DModels\n- Detect relevant elements in the model\n- Calculate routes for cargoes\n\nNon-Functional Requirements:\n- Support models with billions of triangles (60GB)\n- Fast route calculation for hundreds of cargoes",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
