    {
      "id": "GQPAQQ9ORaGzuZxHdpSCL",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 429.26523099147835,
      "y": -851.510741282279,
      "width": 1066.7996826171875,
      "height": 595,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6M",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 285817712,
      "version": 661,
      "versionNonce": 357939056,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1780339848957,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Type-ahead suggestion\n\nWhen a user starts typing in the browser it shows auto-complete suggestions\n\nFunctional Req:\n- Provide auto-complete suggestions with up to 5 records based on prefix X\n- Start auto-complete fetching in the 1st char X\n- Sort suggestions based on frequency of use X\n\nNon-functional reqs:\n- Low latency - completions should be retrieved fastly <200ms x\n- Scale up to millions of RPS X\n- Read intensive >> writes X\n- CAP availability over consistency X\n\nOut-of-scope\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Type-ahead suggestion\n\nWhen a user starts typing in the browser it shows auto-complete suggestions\n\nFunctional Req:\n- Provide auto-complete suggestions with up to 5 records based on prefix X\n- Start auto-complete fetching in the 1st char X\n- Sort suggestions based on frequency of use X\n\nNon-functional reqs:\n- Low latency - completions should be retrieved fastly <200ms x\n- Scale up to millions of RPS X\n- Read intensive >> writes X\n- CAP availability over consistency X\n\nOut-of-scope\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
